## Write a program to convert miles to meters

1 mile = 1609 meters

```txt
Input  : 5
Output : 8046.72
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-miles-to-meters" >

```cpp
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int miles;
    float meter;
    cout<<"enter distance in miles"<<endl;
    cin>>miles;
    meter = miles * 1609.34;
    cout <<"converted from miles to meter\n"<<meter<<" meter\n"; 
    return 0;
}
```

